{"sectionId":763,"sectionIdLiteral":"763","humanId":"lesson-340","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I can be free of suffering today.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 340"},"annotation":"W-340","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-340\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"763#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Father, I thank You for today, and for the freedom I am certain it will bring.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>This day is holy, for today Your Son will be redeemed.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>His suffering is done.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>For he will hear Your Voice directing him to find Christ‚Äôs vision through forgiveness, and be free forever from all suffering.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>Thanks for today, my Father.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>I was born into this world but to achieve this day, and what it holds in joy and freedom for Your holy Son and for the world he made, which is released along with him today.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"763#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Be glad today!</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Be glad!</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>There is no room for anything but joy and thanks today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Our Father has redeemed His Son this day.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#2:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>Not one of us but will be saved today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"763#2:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Not one who will remain in fear, and none the Father will not gather to Himself, awake in Heaven in the Heart of Love.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Father, I thank You for today, and for the freedom I am certain it will bring. This day is holy, for today Your Son will be redeemed. His suffering is done. For he will hear Your Voice directing him","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 340: I can be free of suffering today | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†340 ‚ÄúI can be free of suffering today‚Äù: Father, I thank You for today, and for the freedom I am certain it will bring.‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 340","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":763,"slugs":["lesson-340","i-can-be-free-of-suffering-today"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 340","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":763,"slugs":["lesson-340","i-can-be-free-of-suffering-today"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","